LOS ANGELES COUNTY
LIFEGUARD SERVICE

03:50.926 --> 03:52.754
WITH YOUR MIDDAY BEACH REPORT.

03:52.884 --> 03:56.627
PRESENTLY, THE AIR IS 88
DEGREES, WATER IS 72 DEGREES,

03:56.758 --> 03:58.847
WIND OUT OF THE WEST
AT TEN MILES AN HOUR,

03:58.977 --> 04:00.718
VISIBILITY IS EIGHT MILES.

