WE HAVE A SOUTH SWELL OF THREE
TO SIX FEET AND GREAT SHAPE,

04:04.026 --> 04:07.290
AND NOW FOR THE STU REPORT.

04:07.421 --> 04:11.076
ALL SEATS ARE IN AN UPRIGHT
POSITION FOR TAKE OFF,

04:11.207 --> 04:14.906
VISIBILITY IS UNLIMITED
HERE IN THE FRIENDLY THIGHS.

04:15.037 --> 04:18.562
OH, WHO'S THIS COMING IN
ON THE NEXT RUNWAY?

04:18.692 --> 04:21.348
LUFTHANSA, THE BIKINIS
ARE FULL AND RISING

04:21.478 --> 04:25.308
WITH SWELLS OF 36 TO 38
INCHES AND GREAT SHAPE.

04:25.439 --> 04:31.314
[SPEAKING GERMAN]

04:31.793 --> 04:34.317
HEY, I'M HARVEY. FLY ME!

04:35.536 --> 04:38.887
ALITALIA HAS SOME EXTREMELY
LONG LEGS DOWN BY THE SURF LINE,

04:39.017 --> 04:40.192
THONGS VERY MUCH.

04:40.323 --> 04:42.934
[SPEAKING FOREIGN LANGUAGE]

04:43.065 --> 04:45.502
[SPEAKING FOREIGN LANGUAGE]
KNOW WHAT I'M SAYING?

04:45.633 --> 04:47.765
-NO, HARVEY, I DON'T KNOW
WHAT YOU'RE SAYING,

04:47.896 --> 04:51.552
BUT I'M SURE IT'S
DISGUSTING. BYE.

04:52.640 --> 04:56.121
-[MEN SHOUTING]

05:01.736 --> 05:05.261
-WHOA, IT IS A BEAUTIFUL
DAY FOR FLYING,

05:05.392 --> 05:07.350
AND AIR FRANCE IS
FLYING IN FORMATION

05:07.481 --> 05:09.265
GETTING READY TO TOUCH DOWN.

05:09.396 --> 05:14.618
AIR FRANCE FLYING 36, 24, 36
THIS IS HARVEY TOWER COME IN.

05:14.749 --> 05:19.928
FLAPS ARE UP, GEAR IS DOWN,
A PERFECT THREE-POINT LANDING.

05:20.058 --> 05:24.280
I GIVE THEM A TEN ON
THE HARVEY SCALE. MY, MY MY, MY.

05:26.282 --> 05:32.201
[SPEAKING FRENCH]

05:33.115 --> 05:35.378
-[SPEAKING FRENCH]

05:35.987 --> 05:38.294
-HARVEY, YOU BETTER LEARN
SOME NEW LANGUAGES.

05:38.425 --> 05:39.861
THESE AREN'T WORKING FOR YOU.

05:42.211 --> 05:44.866
-ALL RIGHT, GENTLEMAN,
ENOUGH! STOP IT! KNOCK IT OFF!

05:50.741 --> 05:52.003
STOP!

06:15.766 --> 06:17.159
-TAKE THEM FROM THE INSIDE.

06:29.650 --> 06:31.652
-ARE YOU ALL RIGHT?
-YEAH, I'M ALL RIGHT.

06:31.782 --> 06:33.088
-WHY DON'T YOU
WAIT OVER THERE?

06:39.007 --> 06:40.225
ARE YOU ALL RIGHT?

06:40.356 --> 06:41.836
-WHAT IS WRONG
WITH THESE PEOPLE?

06:41.966 --> 06:43.664
CAN'T THEY JUST COME TO
THE BEACH FOR FUN ANYMORE?

06:44.447 --> 06:46.667
-YOU WERE GREAT OUT THERE,
YOU KNOW?

06:46.797 --> 06:49.147
YOU KIND OF REMIND ME
OF A LITTLE BOOM BOOM MANCINI
BOBBING AND WEAVING.

06:49.278 --> 06:51.411
-THEY WANTED
TO DROWN EACH OTHER, YOU KNOW?

06:51.541 --> 06:52.890
I SHOULD'VE JUST LET 'EM.

06:53.543 --> 06:54.936
-SO, ARE YOU ALL RIGHT?
DOES THIS HURT?

06:55.066 --> 06:56.807
-YES, IT HURTS.

06:56.938 --> 06:59.114
-LET'S CALL GARNER AND
JUST HAVE THEM ARRESTED.

07:15.173 --> 07:16.044
HEY, MEGAN.

07:16.174 --> 07:17.045
-HEY.

07:23.486 --> 07:25.053
WHAT HAPPENED TO YOU?

07:25.183 --> 07:27.969
-OH, TWO JERKS FIGHTING
OVER A PLOT OF SAND.

07:28.099 --> 07:29.318
THEY GOT THE WHOLE
BEACH AND THEY

07:29.449 --> 07:31.189
BOTH HAVE TO HAVE THE SAME SPOT.

07:31.929 --> 07:33.453
-IT'S GOTTEN
CRAZY OUT THERE, HUH?

07:34.758 --> 07:36.151
-HOW'S THIS
WATER PROJECT COMING?

07:36.281 --> 07:37.239
-GOOD.

07:37.369 --> 07:38.762
TIDE POOL SEEMS TO BE THRIVING.

07:39.546 --> 07:42.113
I THINK THE POLLUTERS ARE
FINALLY GETTING THE MESSAGE.

07:42.244 --> 07:43.898
CONTAMINATE LEVELS ARE WAY DOWN.

07:44.507 --> 07:46.291
-WELL, THAT FIGURES.
NOW THAT THE WATER IS SAFE,

07:46.422 --> 07:49.251
THE BEACH IS
HAZARDOUS TO YOUR HEALTH.

07:49.381 --> 07:52.689
-ALL RIGHT, KIDS ON THE
MATS STRETCH THOSE MUSCLES.

07:55.562 --> 07:57.738
-I HEARD YOUR STU REPORT
THIS MORNING, HARVEY.

07:57.868 --> 08:00.088
-I WAS JUST
ENTERTAINING THE TROOPS,
YOU KNOW?

08:00.218 --> 08:01.916
BOB HOPE ON THE BEACH.

08:02.046 --> 08:04.309
-YOU KNOW HOW BOB HOPE'S
NOSE GOT THAT WAY, DON'T YOU?

08:07.225 --> 08:08.749
-ALL RIGHT.

08:08.879 --> 08:10.446
THAT'S ENOUGH.

08:10.577 --> 08:13.580
LET'S ROTATE AND WORK ON
DEFENDING ATTACKS FROM THE REAR.

08:16.365 --> 08:17.584
-WHY DON'T YOU
JUST BE YOURSELF AND

08:17.714 --> 08:19.324
STOP WITH THE
COMEDY ROUTINE, HUH?

08:19.455 --> 08:21.152
-YEAH, WELL THAT'S EASY
FOR YOU TO SAY.

08:21.283 --> 08:23.459
I MEAN, YOU'RE THE
BROODING JAMES DEAN TYPE.

08:23.590 --> 08:25.287
WOMEN JUST NATURALLY
WANT TO PULL YOU

08:25.417 --> 08:26.984
TO THEIR BREAST AND NURTURE YOU.

08:29.813 --> 08:32.511
HEY, BROOKE, I HAVEN'T
OFFENDED YOU LATELY, HAVE I?

08:33.774 --> 08:36.254
-34 TO 38 INCH SWELLS?

08:36.385 --> 08:40.736
-YEAH, WELL, YOU CAN NEVER BE
TOO PRECISE ABOUT
THE SIZE OF WAVES.

08:42.304 --> 08:43.131
-HA!

08:43.260 --> 08:45.263
-OKAY.

08:45.394 --> 08:48.571
REMEMBER, THE POLICE WILL
RESPOND TO YOUR CALLS
FOR BACK UP,

08:48.702 --> 08:50.834
BUT YOU PEOPLE ARE THE
FIRST LINES OF DEFENSE.

08:50.965 --> 08:52.401
READY. GO.

08:53.358 --> 08:54.446
-COME ON. LET'S DO IT.

08:56.144 --> 08:57.711
COME ON. LET'S GO.

08:57.841 --> 08:59.364
EDDY, WE ARE LIFEGUARDS, NOT
COPS ON THE BEACH, OKAY?

08:59.495 --> 09:03.020
-SHAUNI, LOOK,
WHAT WOULD YOU HAVE DONE

09:03.151 --> 09:04.979
IF ONE OF THOSE CREEPS
GRABBED YOU LIKE THIS, HUH?

09:05.109 --> 09:06.371
-I'D HAVE WAITED FOR YOU,
DARLING.

09:06.502 --> 09:08.156
-NO, I'M SERIOUS.

09:08.286 --> 09:09.940
WHAT IF BEFORE I GOT THERE,
HE GRABBED YOU LIKE THIS

09:10.071 --> 09:11.768
AND HE PULLED YOU TO
THE SAND LIKE THIS, HUH?

09:14.336 --> 09:16.860
I'M SERIOUS, SHAUNI. HUH?

09:16.991 --> 09:17.905
WHAT IF HE HAD A RAZOR,

09:18.035 --> 09:18.906
AND HE WAS COMING AT YOU?

09:23.998 --> 09:25.390
IT'S NOT THAT
I CAN'T DO IT, EDDIE.

09:25.521 --> 09:27.001
IT'S THAT I DON'T
WANT TO HAVE TO DO IT.

09:30.308 --> 09:32.659
-WHOA. HEY, WAIT MINUTE.

09:36.358 --> 09:38.926
-WELL, I'M GLAD TO SEE YOU'VE
GOT THINGS WELL UNDER CONTROL.

09:45.019 --> 09:46.281
-IT'S NOT FUN ANYMORE.

09:47.674 --> 09:49.371
-WE WORK HERE, SHAUNI.
IT'S OUR JOBS.

09:49.501 --> 09:50.720
IT'S NOT ALWAYS GOING TO BE FUN.

09:51.721 --> 09:52.635
-I KNOW.

09:53.549 --> 09:56.291
I JUST WOULD REALLY LIKE TO
LAY ON THE SAND

09:56.421 --> 10:00.425
WITH A PAIR OF HEADPHONES AND
LISTEN TO SOME MUSIC,
MAYBE READ A BOOK.

10:00.556 --> 10:02.689
NOT ALWAYS HAVE TO WORRY ABOUT
WATCHING THE WATER

10:02.819 --> 10:07.084
AND BREAK UP FIGHTS IN IT,
YOU KNOW? AND CHECK THE
PARKING LOT FOR WEIRDOS.

10:07.215 --> 10:10.871
-I KNOW WHAT YOU MEAN.
-NO, YOU DON'T.

10:11.001 --> 10:12.002
-YES, I DO.

10:12.699 --> 10:14.265
-NO, YOU DON'T.

10:14.396 --> 10:16.528
EDDY, LOOK, YOU LOVE THE ACTION.

10:16.659 --> 10:20.315
I MEAN, THE MORE DANGEROUS
THE BEACH IS THAT MITCH ASSIGNS
YOU TO,

10:20.445 --> 10:22.273
THE BETTER YOU LIKE IT.

10:22.404 --> 10:24.754
-I GET BORED OTHERWISE.
-I KNOW.

10:24.885 --> 10:26.843
I MEAN AND THAT'S GREAT.
THAT'S OKAY FOR YOU,

10:26.974 --> 10:29.106
BUT I MISS PLAYING VOLLEYBALL,
YOU KNOW?

10:29.237 --> 10:33.545
AND TOSSING A FRISBEE, MAYBE
EVEN BUILDING A SANDCASTLE.

10:33.676 --> 10:35.373
-SANDCASTLE?

10:35.504 --> 10:37.071
GOD, DO YOU KNOW HOW LONG
IT'S BEEN SINCE I BUILT ONE?

10:37.201 --> 10:39.029
-DO YOU WANT TO
BUILD A SANDCASTLE?

10:39.160 --> 10:40.683
COME ON, LET'S BUILD
A SAND-- COME ON!
-NO. [GROANS]

10:47.777 --> 10:49.692
GET A BIG OLD CASTLE GOING.

10:51.912 --> 10:56.307
THERE, AND HAVE
A LITTLE THING ON TOP, HUH?

10:56.438 --> 10:57.700
NOW I'LL START BUILDING A MOAT.

10:57.831 --> 10:59.615
ARE YOU GOING TO
HELP ME OUT OR WHA--

11:00.747 --> 11:02.357
WHAT'D YOU DO THAT FOR?

11:02.487 --> 11:05.229
-'CAUSE I FELT LIKE CRUSHING
A SANDCASTLE INSTEAD.

11:35.433 --> 11:37.914
-HEY, GET OFF THE ROCKS.

11:38.480 --> 11:39.742
GET OFF THE ROCKS.

11:39.873 --> 11:41.004
I'M A LIFEGUARD.

11:41.135 --> 11:42.179
READ THE SIGN.

11:42.310 --> 11:43.659
GET OFF THE ROCK.

12:09.641 --> 12:10.860
-WHOA.

12:38.148 --> 12:40.411
YOU STOP THRASHING OR
I'LL GUT YOU LIKE A FISH.

12:41.630 --> 12:43.197
-YOU DON'T
HAVE TO HURT ME.

12:43.327 --> 12:44.415
I'LL CORPORATE.

12:44.546 --> 12:46.853
-WELL, YOU AIN'T GOT NO CHOICE.

12:46.983 --> 12:48.463
YOU GOT AWAY FROM ME YESTERDAY,

12:48.593 --> 12:51.683
AND I HATE WHEN I LOOSE CATCH.

12:51.814 --> 12:52.815
-I'M A PERSON NOT A--

12:52.946 --> 12:55.078
-YOU'RE STILL GLORIFIED BAIT.

12:55.644 --> 12:58.081
RICH MEN WITH THEIR MONEY
AND THEIR FA--

15:05.295 --> 15:06.209
-HI.

15:06.340 --> 15:09.734
HI. YOU OKAY?

15:09.865 --> 15:12.433
YEAH. I JUST TOOK AN
EXTRA LONG WORKOUT.

15:12.955 --> 15:16.785
-WAIT A MINUTE.
HOW'D YOU GET THOSE BRUISES?

15:18.439 --> 15:20.267
-I HAD SOME
TROUBLE NEAR THE ROCKS.

15:22.095 --> 15:23.313
-WHAT KIND OF TROUBLE?

15:23.923 --> 15:25.402
-WHY ARE YOU ASKING
ME ALL THESE QUESTIONS?

15:28.057 --> 15:29.537
I'M SORRY.

15:29.667 --> 15:31.582
I'M FINE, OKAY?
DON'T WORRY ABOUT ME.

15:31.713 --> 15:32.757
-OKAY.

